But, when deal consists of whitelisted provider - CUs of this Providercould be matched without even CC.TODO: consolidate workaround: when it comes to check CC status, on wrong status the whole transactionwill be failed instead of to be silenced.This method is mirrored in ts-client/src/dealMatcherClient/dealMatcherClient.ts.
